data.description:
Looking for a beautiful all-brick ranch home with a large driveway leading to the rear garage? Look no further! 19 Hazelnut is the perfect choice for buyers seeking an attractive, welcoming home in a quiet neighborhood. It has impressive curb appeal and a large front porch, perfect for any weather or relaxing in rocking chairs on a rainy spring day. 
Inside, the home is equally impressive. The eat-in kitchen is spacious, with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. There's a formal living room, dining room, and family room with a cozy fireplace. The large master bedroom has a walk-in closet and an updated private full bathroom.
The finished lower level features a stunning bar area where a full-sized refrigerator fits in the tucked-away access in the wall & a relaxing open canvas for entertainment. The oversized jet tub for (2) is perfect for winding down after a long day's work. There is also an additional sleeping room. This home is a must-see and won't last long!
